## Nonzero derivative analytic functions are locally injective

This is a straightforward consequence of the inverse function theorem.  We also prove
parameterized versions, where `f : ‚ÑÇ ‚Üí S ‚Üí T`.
-/

open Classical
open Filter (Tendsto)
